                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The khravgodon is reduced below 70 HP</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The khravgodon collapses. It is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] and can use actions that require only its mind, but any other action ends the ruse.</p>\n<p>A successful @Check[type:perception|dc:18|traits:action:seek] check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Seek] or @Check[type:medicine|dc:18|traits:action:recall-knowledge] check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Recall Knowledge] is required to determine that the animal is not, in fact, dead.</p>"
